    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini nostri Iesu Christi dei eterni. <persName ref="#people/9"
                            key="#Emperor/king">Lotharius</persName> divina ordinante providentia
                            <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs> augustus. Si petitionibus
                        fidelium nostrorum, quas nostris auribus patefaciunt, libenter annuimus et
                        eas ad effectum perducimus, hoc nobis procul dubio ad mercedis nostre
                        augmentum et eternam beatitudinem capescendam pertinere confidimus. Idcirco
                        notum sit omnibus fidelibus sancte dei ecclesie ac nostris presentibus et
                        futuris, quia <persName ref="#people/1653" key="#Consiliarius_regis"
                            >Haimo</persName> devotissimus atque fidelis <rs
                            key="#Consiliarius_regis">consiliarius</rs> noster adiens serenitatem
                        culminis nostri ostendit nobis <rs key="#Immunity">quasdam auctoritates
                            immunitatis</rs> avi nostri <persName ref="#people/14">Karoli</persName>
                        bone memorie ac genitoris nostri <persName ref="#people/118"
                            >Ludouici</persName>, in quibus continebatur insertum, qualiter <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterium</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/301" key="#Immunity #Monasteries">sancti
                            Salvatoris</orgName>, quod est situm in <placeName ref="#places/737"
                            >Monte Amiato</placeName> in territorio <placeName ref="#places/3505"
                            >Clusino</placeName>, sub eorum immunitatis defensione susceperunt,
                        deprecans, ut et nos pro firmitatis gratia super easdem nostram addere non
                        denegaremus auctoritatem. Cuius petitioni libenter assensum prebuimus et
                        hanc nostram auctoritatem circa idem monasterium fieri decernimus, per quam
                        precipimus atque iubemus, ut nullus iudex publicus vel quislibet ex
                        iudiciaria potestate in ecclesias aut loca vel agros seu reliquas
                        possessiones memorati monasterii, quas moderno tempore iuste et legaliter
                        possidet vel que deinceps ad iura ipsius loci divina pietas voluerit augeri,
                        ad causas audiendas vel freda exigenda aut mansiones vel paratas faciendas
                        aut fideiussores tollendos aut homines ipsius monasterii tam ingenuos quam
                        et servos super terram ipsius commanentes distringendos nec ullas
                        redibitiones aut illicitas occasiones requirendas nostris et futuris
                        temporibus ingredi audeat vel ea, que supra memorata sunt, penitus exigere
                        presumat. Continebatur etiam in eisdem auctoritatibus, qualiter avus et
                        genitor noster res quasdam ad ipsum monasterium confirmassent, id est <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/1511"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ><placeName ref="#places/1944" key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches">sancti Petri in
                            Garmarita</placeName></orgName> consistentem atque <rs
                            key="#Cells/hermitages">cellam</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/1454" key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"><placeName ref="#places/1947" key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches">sancti
                                Sabini</placeName></orgName> et <orgName
                                    ref="#juridical_persons/1452" key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"><placeName ref="#places/1946" key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches">sancte
                                Restitute</placeName></orgName> vel <orgName
                                    ref="#juridical_persons/1456" key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"><placeName ref="#places/1945" key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches">sancti
                                        Petri</placeName></orgName> seu et <placeName ref="#places/1948" key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                            ><orgName ref="#juridical_persons/1455" key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches">sancti
                            Stefani</orgName></placeName> in <placeName ref="#places/430"
                                >Tarquino</placeName> vel <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/308" key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><placeName ref="#places/762" key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches">sancti Salvatoris in
                                Rumiliano</placeName></orgName> atque <orgName
                                    ref="#juridical_persons/303" key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches">sancti Stefani in <placeName
                                        ref="#places/757" key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches">Monticulo</placeName></orgName> sive <orgName
                                            ref="#juridical_persons/1513" key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches">sancti Seueri in <placeName
                                                ref="#places/1950" key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches">Paterno</placeName></orgName>, pariter cum earum
                        omnium adiacentiis vel pertinentiis. Quas etiam, sicut supra diximus, simili
                        modo confirmamus, ut nulla eidem huiusmodi calumpnia inferatur, sed liceat
                        ei suisque successoribus res predicti monasterii cum omnibus ad se iuste et
                        legaliter aspicientibus vel pertinentibus sub immunitatis nostre defensione
                        quieto ordine possidere. Et ut hec auctoritas confirmationis nostre firmior
                        videatur atque in omnibus meliorem obtineat vigorem, manu propria
                        confirmavimus et anuli nostri impressione adsigniri iussimus. Signum (M.)
                        Lotharii serenissimi augusti. Data sexto klas. novemb. anno Christo propitio
                        imperii domni Lotharii pii imperatoris octavo decimo, indictione prima;
                        actum <placeName ref="#places/65" key="#Cities #Palatium">Papia</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Cities">civitate</rs>
                        <rs key="#Palatium">palatio</rs> regis; in dei nomine feliciter amen.</ab>
                </div>
